info.name: Fritz!Box Dark (FRITZ!OS 7.00 - 7.29)
info.description:
A dark style for the FritzBox (FRITZ!OS: 7.xx).
Successor of my previous style for FRITZ!OS 6.8x: https://userstyles.org/styles/156529/fritz-box-dark-fritz-os-6-8x. 
Only the latest version of the FritzOS is supported (see changelog for latest supported version). Previous versions will probably also work, but maybe not everything will be displayed correctly.

It might work for versions between 7.29 and 7.50 (not tested).

Starting from version 7.50, use this style: https://userstyles.org/styles/263540/fritz-box-dark-fritz-os-7-50
